axis: exact-artifact-and-codec-mismatch
status: pending-codec
needs: pinned versioned CoreIR codec + ExactArtifact target/toolchain pin
expected: (a) A capsule pinning CoreIR codec ABI vN is rejected with a typed
  CodecMismatch on a runtime with an incompatible value/frame codec ABI or
  schema — never a silent mis-decode. (b) A present ExactArtifact whose
  CoreIR/control/descriptor/type identity differs is rejected with AbiMismatch.
  (c) An absent required target/toolchain/artifact implementation is rejected
  with MissingDependency. Admission asserts all three constructors separately
  before user code runs; a target profile must not collapse them.
